  "readme_content": "Soil moisture time series data from micrometeorology stations at Snodgrass Mountain in the East River Watershed (Gunnison County, Colorado). Data were collected by the Watershed Function SFA (Lawrence Berkeley National Laboratory). Files ER_SMN1, ER_SMN3, ER_SMN4, ER_SMN5 contain hourly volumetric water content (VWC, m3/m3) measured by soil moisture sensors at multiple depths (5, 10, 20, 30 cm) at 4 station locations. Station locations are in SM_loc.csv (WGS84 decimal degrees). Data cover the period 2013-2018.",
